Title: A COMPARISON OF TWO PARADIGMS FOR DISTRIBUTED SHARED MEMORY measurements show that both paradigms can
Author: Willem G. Levelt M. Frans Kaashoek Henri E. Bal Andrew S. Tanenbaum 
Keyword: Amoeba Distributed shared memory Distributed programming Orca Shared data-objects Shared Virtual Memory  
